Introduction:
Thank you for choosing Privacy Guard. This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you about the types of information we may collect from you when you use our application, how we use that information, and the measures we take to keep your data secure. By using Privacy Guard, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect:

Permission Information:

Privacy Guard is designed to inspect and display the permissions used by other applications on your device. The app itself does not collect or store any personal information about you.
Device Information:

To provide accurate permission details, Privacy Guard may access device information such as device model, operating system version, and other relevant details. This information is used solely for the purpose of app functionality.
Information Usage:

No Internet Usage:

Privacy Guard operates entirely offline and does not require an internet connection to function. We do not collect, transmit, or share any information about your device or app permissions over the internet.
User Data Is Not Shared:

Privacy Guard does not share any user information with third parties. All permission details and device information remain stored locally on your device and are not transmitted to external servers.
Data Security:

Local Storage:

Permission details and device information are stored locally on your device and are not shared externally. We prioritize the security of your data and have implemented measures to prevent unauthorized access.
No User Accounts:

Privacy Guard does not require user accounts, login credentials, or any personal identifiers. Your privacy is essential to us, and we have designed the app to operate without collecting unnecessary personal information.
Updates to Privacy Policy:

Policy Revisions:
This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices or the functionality of the app. Users will be notified of any significant changes to this policy.


Conclusion:
Privacy Guard is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your data. By using our app, you can trust that your information is handled with the utmost care and in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

Thank you for choosing Privacy Guard.

Sincerely,

Privacy Guard Team



